{%- comment -%}
Snippet: Header Navigation (Desktop Right)
Descrition: This is the right side of the header navigation for desktop.
            It is a loop that goes through the main menu linklist and renders the links.

Usage:
  {% render 'header-navigation', menu: menu %}

Access:
  main_menu_linklist
{%- endcomment -%}

<ul class="header-navigation header-navigation--right flex flex-row items-center h-full w-full">
  {% for link in menu %}
    <li class="mr-5 xl:mr-6">
      <a
        href="{{ link.url }}"
        aria-label="{{ 'general.check_out' | t }} {{ link.title }}"
        class="text-nav-font font-medium uppercase link link--reversed">
        {{ link.title }}
      </a>
    </li>
  {% endfor %}
</ul>
